&lt;p&gt;Waymark is a team of healthcare providers, technologists, and builders whose mission is to bring the best healthcare to people with Medicaid benefits.&amp;nbsp; Guided by the communities we serve, we bring support and technology-enabled care to help primary care providers keep Medicaid patients healthy.&amp;nbsp; We are building the tools and designing an approach to enable care to reach the patients who can benefit most.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
